<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_473a5388-f3b3-4706-8148-a17ee17f07cc" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B7P4</sptc><title id="_1b182015-7344-4fe8-826a-95f0a92f8fae">Isolation</title><archive-num><placeholder outputclass="placeholder">[ARCHIVE]</placeholder></archive-num><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10756_0.3.0.xml" variation="TAS" variation-type="REPLACE">TAS REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_72bff792-627c-4daf-91a3-72dd8a9c97fe" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a9cf203d-c59c-4e0a-bb23-b60b6f1ba866">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Means of isolation must be provided to a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/4891_0.8.0.xml#_a8d909a0-d649-477d-a969-848c9187c05d" id="_c6a20b91-29b7-421d-805e-e49b7d234fb9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rainwater storage</xref> and components that require testing, maintenance, or replacement including mechanical devices, appliances and controls.</p></subclause><callout id="_26b8b689-0f8e-4717-a507-193373511658"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption"/><p>B7P4 does not apply to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1463_0.4.0.xml#_fb3536f6-7ee5-4a29-a4da-402a8e1168dc" id="_d33feab0-40c9-4e14-8302-64ed58a295f4" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">site</xref> not provided with a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1250_0.7.0.xml#_762d6a54-e28c-400b-b9c5-5fceac019a05" id="_07d7157f-c161-4b54-82f1-7169ac720015" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drinking water</xref> service by a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_19f47b6e-a7f3-4b06-8d4d-1e2c7b400d7d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref>.</p></callout><callout id="_6f7a854b-ca72-424d-9706-3616d01f1142"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Isolation valves are a means of providing isolation.</p></callout></clause>